.TP
.BI \(hyL " localkey\fR, " --local-keyfile " localkey"
Specify the local keyfile to use to sign database
files and reports.
.TP
.BI \(hyS " sitekey\fR, " --site-keyfile " sitekey"
Specify the site keyfile to use to sign configuration
