.TP
.BI \(hyP " passphrase\fR, " --local-passphrase " passphrase"
Specify the passphrase to use when signing with the 
local keyfile.
.TP
.BI \(hyQ " passphrase\fR, " --site-passphrase " passphrase"
Specify the passphrase to use when signing with the 
site keyfile.
.TP
